Given the general system description: The user would like to build a system called pacemaker, where Pacemaker: heart beats every 5 ticks. If heart stops, pacemaker detects within 2 ticks and delivers pacing pulse.. There are 2 processes in the system, the descriptions of the processes are as follows: Heart: Heart beats naturally every 5 time units.; Pacemaker: Monitors heartbeat. If heart stops, delivers pace within 2 ticks., now generate the PAT code corresponding to the **following system annotation**. Refer to the system description **only** if explicitly guided in the annotation, or if there is a contradiction between the annotation and the description.

